	<annex id="annex-matrix-guidance" obligation="normative"><title>MATRIX GUIDANCE</title><clause id="_introduction_9" obligation="normative"><title>Introduction</title><p id="_4e6dc2d3-24d6-4707-b1e1-9a5088a9d04f">The <xref target="scl-matrix-description">Matrix</xref>, as presented in <xref target="scl-matrix"/>, includes a range of selectable criteria for hydrographic survey parameters / data types. It is organised by the following data classes: Bathymetry, Other Positioning, Water Flow, and Nature of the Bottom.</p>
